<pre class="bz_comment_text" >The patch in <span class=""><a href="attachment.cgi?id=829037&amp;action=diff" name="attach_829037" title="disarm mysql_install_db default behaviour">attachment 829037</a> <a href="attachment.cgi?id=829037&amp;action=edit" title="disarm mysql_install_db default behaviour">[details]</a></span> will remove the dangerous behaviour of
